Key Match Events: Adam Zampa wins Man of the Match for his 3/21.
Australia won the match by 33 runs and inch closer to a place in the semi-final.
England scored 44 runs off the last 3 overs with 2 wickets in hand.
Pre-Game Insights: Australia are in third place and have a bright chance for the semi-finals. But the defending champions, England, have a contrasting tournament. They are at the bottom of the table and need to win their remaining games to qualify for the ICC Champions Trophy 2025 in Pakistan.
